== Faction ==
[[Mercenary Guild]]

== Location ==
The Praetor can be hired from the [[Outpost|Mercenary Guild Outpost]] in [[Vulcore]] for 12 mercreds.

== Combat Strategy ==
A devastating frontline siege unit, the Praetor combines sustained firepower with shield disruption to crack through enemy defenses. Though it lacks personal shielding, its raw durability and power make it a reliable anchor for any squad.

